    "data": "اَلسَّلاَمُ عَلَيْكَ يَا وَلِیَّ اللهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ عَلَيْكَ يَا حُجَّةَ اللهِ وَ خَالِصَتَهٗ اَلسَّلاَمُ عَلَيْكَ يَا اِمَامَ الْمُوْمِنِيْنَ وَ وَارِثَ الْمُرْسَلِيْنَ وَ حُجَّةَ رَبِّ الْعَالَمِيْنَ صَلَّی اللهُ عَلَيْكَ وَ عَلٰی اٰلِ بَيْتِكَ الطَّيِّبِيْنَ الطَّاهِرِيْنَ يَا مَوْلاَیَ يَا اَبَا مُحَمَّدٍ الْحَسَنَ بْنَ عَلِیٍّ اَنَا مَوْلًی لَكَ وَلِآلِ بَيْتِكَ وَ هٰذَا يَوْمُكَ وَ هُوَ يَوْمُ الْخَمِيْسِ وَ اَنَا ضَيْفُكَ فِيْهِ وَ مُسْتَجِيْرٌ بِكَ فِيْهِ فَاَحْسِنْ ضِيَافَتِیْ وَ اِجَارَتِیْ بِحَقِّ اٰلِ بَيْتِكَ الطَّيِّبِيْنَ الطَّاهِرِيْنَ.\nASSALAAMO A’LAYKA YAA WALIYYAL LAAHE ASSALAAMO A’LAYKA YAA HUJJATAL LAAHE WA KHAALESATAHU ASSALAAMO A’LAYKA YAA EMAAMAL MOMENEENA WA WAARESAL MURSALEENA WA HUJJATA RABBIL A’ALAMEENA SALLAL LAAHO A’LAYKA WA A’LAA AALE BAYTEKAT TAYYEBEENAT TAAHEREENA YAA MAWLAAYA YAA ABAA MOHAMMADENIL HASANABNA A’LIYYE ANAA MAWLAN LAKA WA LE AALE BAYTEKA WA HAAZAA YAWMOKA WA HOWA YAWMUL KHAMEESE WA ANAA ZAYFOKA FEEHE WA MUSTAJEERUN BEKA FEEHE FA-AHSIN ZEYAAFATEE WA EJAARATEE BE-HAQQE AALE BAYTEKAT TAYYEBEENAT TAAHEREENA.\nPeace be on you, O intimate friend of Allah Peace be on you, O the decisive argument of Allah, sincerely attached to Him Peace be on you, O Guide-Leader of the faithfuls inheritor of the Apostles, clear convincing sign of the Lord of the worlds, blessings of Allah be on you, and on your pure and pious children. O Master, O Abu Mohammad, Hasan son of Ali, I am your obedient follower and of your children, today is your day, Thursday, I come near you today seek your close friendship receive me with open arms, and keep me close, for the sake of your pure and pious children.", 
    "title": "Ziyarah of Imam Hasan al Askari (a) on Thursday"
